Package com.fasterxml.clustermate.service.msg

Package that contains server-side service abstractions for POJOs used for response Objects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StreamingResponseContent
    Interface wrapped around content that is dynamically read and written as part of Service response processing.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CRUDResponseBase<K extends EntryKey>
    Base class used by various response messages (mostly errors, but not just them) used with main CRD operations (single-entry create/retrive/delete) used so caller can try to extract more specific error information, beyond HTTP status code.
    DeleteResponse<K extends EntryKey>
    POJO returned as a result of successful DELETE request (which ideally should be any and all DELETE requests)
    ErrorResponse
    Entity used for errors for operations other than CRUD.
    GetErrorResponse<K extends EntryKey>
    Simple POJO used for enclosing information in case of a failed GET
    PutResponse<K extends EntryKey>
    Simple value class used to return information on a successful PUT request
    StreamingResponseContentImpl
    Simple (but not naive) StreamingResponseContent implementation used for returning content for inlined entries.
